title: Eps. 91 - Grandma's Gun
description:
We’re 13 days into the 100 Day Challenge and the guys are talking about how the challenge is going. While the challenge has been very impactful in all areas the guys specifically talk about how they’re being impacted in the family category. They also talk about the importance of building new habits and how doing things that are of high value will help you create the proper habits. Creating the right habits that will help you create a quality life and that is part of what the 100 Day Challenge is about. It’s not too late to join us just visit 100 Day Challenge With ET.
